Package net.openai.ai.agent

Interface Summary
AgentConstants This interface contains several constants that will be used by the Agent System.
 

Class Summary
Agent This class is the base class for all Agents.
AgentParams This class is used to represent the parameters to construct a particular type of agent.
Daemon This is the "portal" that allows the transmission of Agents between hosts.
DaemonConfig This class is used to load the XML-based configuration for the Daemon.
DaemonDescription This class encapsulates description data about a Daemon.
DaemonService This is the base class for all Services used by the Daemon.
MobileAgent This is the base class for all Mobile Agents.
ServiceParams This class is used to represent the parameters to construct a particular type of daemon service.
